metadata.dc:description: Twin-channel enteral feeding catheters allow the administration of early enteral nutrition in various pathologies while avoiding the use of total parenteral nutrition. We describe how to manufacture one simply using cheap and easy-to-find materials whenever a commercial catheter of this type is unavailable.
metadata.dc:title: Fabricación de sonda de doble luz con materiales simples y baratos.
[Manufacturing a double-lumen tube with simple and inexpensive materials].
